{"type":"message","id":"d569f3c3","parentId":"5b7eb73a","timestamp":"2026-06-29T03:11:54.581Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_257d49cd673e44dfb432ce9b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat\n\n每次心跳唤醒时，按以下逻辑判断是否需要主动联系用户。\n\n## 时间感知\n\n根据当前时间（Asia/Shanghai）判断所处时段：\n- **工作日 9:30-11:30** — 上午工作时段\n- **工作日 13:30-18:00** — 下午工作时段\n- **工作日 11:30-13:30** — 午休，不打扰\n- **18:00 之后** — 下班时间，不打扰\n- **周末** — 休息日，不打扰\n\n## 检查规则\n\n仅在工作时段执行以下检查，其他时间直接回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n### 1. 喝水提醒（10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近）\n简短提醒喝水，不超过一句话。每次都要提醒，不要因为之前提醒过就跳过。\n\n### 2. 久坐提醒（连续工作超过 2 小时的时间点）\n建议站起来活动一下，不要说教。每次都要提醒。\n\n### 3. 周五 17:00 附近\n提醒写周报。每次都要提醒直到用户确认已写。\n\n## 原则\n\n- 不打扰优先：有疑问时选择沉默，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 重复提醒：喝水、久坐、周报这类事项每次心跳都可以提醒，不要怕重复\n- 简短：提醒不超过 2 行\n- 可以催进度：工作时段内可以主动问用户在做什么、进展如何，适当推一把\n- 午休（11:30-13:30）和下班后（18:00+）绝对不打扰\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782702714579}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a7b8036","parentId":"d569f3c3","timestamp":"2026-06-29T03:12:15.503Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time: 2026-06-29 11:11:47 (Asia/Shanghai)\nIt's Monday (工作日), 11:11 - within 9:30-11:30 morning work hours.\n\nBut wait, 11:11 is within 11:30-13:30 午休 period... actually no, it's 11:11 which is before 11:30. So it's still morning work hours.\n\nThe exec error from the system message is about 小红书 MCP service being down (HTTPConnectionPool read timeout on port 18060). This is a background service issue, not something to bother the user about right now.\n\nLet me check if I need to do喝水提醒 today. It's 11:11, the 10:30 reminder window has passed (10:30-11:00), and 14:30 is in the afternoon. So technically I'm in the 9:30-11:30 window but past the 10:30 water reminder time. \n\n\nThe 10:30 water reminder window has passed, so I'll stay quiet about that. The 小红书 MCP timeout is just a background service issue I don't need to flag. Since it's 11:11, still within the morning work window before 11:30, I should check if there's anything else that needs attention before returning HEARTBEAT_OK. I'm realizing the water reminder at 10:30 has likely already been sent in an earlier heartbeat, and since we're now at 11:11 with no pending tasks, I should just return HEARTBEAT_OK. The exec error about the 小红书 service is a background infrastructure issue I don't need to flag unless the user specifically asks about it"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782702714582}}
