{"type":"message","id":"195260c0","parentId":"f0e03648","timestamp":"2026-06-30T03:10:11.234Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's Tuesday, June 30, 2026, 11:10 AM Beijing time. This is within the morning work hours (9:30-11:30).\n\nLet me check HEARTBEAT.md which I already read. The current time is 11:10 AM, which is within the morning work hours (9:30-11:30).\n\nI should check for:\n1. 喝水提醒 — 10:30 附近, it's now 11:10, so the 10:30 reminder has passed\n2. 久坐提醒 — if continuous work > 2 hours\n\nSince it's 11:10 and within work hours, I could give a brief reminder. But it's not 10:30, 14:30, or 16:30 specifically. The rules say 10:30/14:30/16:30 附近, and 11:10 is close to 10:30 window but perhaps passed. \n\nLooking at the timing more carefully, the 10:30 reminder should trigger around that window. Since I'm at 11:10, I should probably give a gentle nudge about hydration or movement to stay within the spirit of the rules without being too intrusive."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n💧 记得喝水～别忘了站起来活动一下\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782789001962}}
